{"tid":776863,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"木吉下弦枕一問","createTime":"2018-08-12T12:32:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T02:40:05.000Z","uid":181796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d23cfa3cadc7bfc67ac4bd4abbbbad203bcd4340","tid":776863,"uid":181796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"話說小弟最近拎左支木吉出去做set up<br />\n<br />\n個師傅一見到我支吉他就問我係咪買左二手吉他<br />\n<br />\n佢話正常一支吉他既下弦枕唔會加墊片，應該係一塊過<br />\n<br />\n只有係大陸廠造既低質吉他先有機會加墊片，仲話我塊弦<br />\n<br />\n枕個底都唔平衡添，講個陣仲露出一個狗也不屌既表情<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無ching知佢講既真定假？<br />\n（支吉他大概2000$，購自小學雞吉他網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n附圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/202938_03cc54f7a9e34fb6589b74476ca511e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F202938_03cc54f7a9e34fb6589b74476ca511e5.png&h=e35ab64f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/203224_3be50978eaa869359593e8953673e5a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F203224_3be50978eaa869359593e8953673e5a3.png&h=2563a2db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"668618440714915c15bf9fd2515958a5616eddda","tid":776863,"uid":117991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T02:40:05.000Z","msg":"jab <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}